markdownContent: «I guess that makes sense! You've been a great help! It's sometimes so difficult to tell anything just based on information in the data-set, so a picture would've been very useful, even though it can be misleading sometimes. Guess you can't beat having the object in front of you. It's just something different, if you're able to touch it, feel the weight… but I'm starting to ramble. Frederic asked for you, I think he has another task for you or something. Thank you so much again for your help!»
